 
                How to fry a player (or yerself)
 
        a) Make sure the chair is energized.
                'push breaker'    
        b) After that, strap the victim in the chair.
                'strap straps to <victim>'
        c) If the victim is too noisy, gag em!
                'gag <victim>'
        d) Pull the lever and fry the sucker!
                'pull lever'
        e) Victim can be freed by:
                'unstrap straps from <victim>'
 
